data.description:
Welcome to the listing for 3553 Inverrary Blvd, Lauderhill, FL 33319! This stunning townhome is located in a gated community and offers a host of desirable features and amenities. With a new roof completed in 2021 and a range of recent upgrades, this property is sure to impress.As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh paint throughout the interior, giving the home a bright and modern feel. The spacious living area is perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing after a long day. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a true highlight of this townhome. It has been completely renovated with new stainless steel appliances, new kitchen cabinets, and stunning granite countertops with an island. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking for family and friends, this kitchen is sure to exceed your expectations.

Upstairs, you'll find the master bedroom, complete with a walk-in closet and a luxurious whirlpool tub. This private retreat offers a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The additional bedrooms are also spacious and well-appointed, providing plenty of room for family members or guests.

Outside, the rear patio offers a great space for outdoor dining, relaxing, or hosting barbecues. It's the perfect spot to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather year-round.

The community itself boasts a range of amenities, including two public pools and tennis courts. Whether you're looking to cool off on a hot summer day or engage in some friendly competition, these amenities provide endless opportunities for fun and relaxation.

Located in Lauderhill, this townhome offers convenient access to a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options. With easy access to major highways, commuting to work or exploring the surrounding areas is a breeze.

Don't miss your chance to own this incredible townhome in a desirable gated community. With its new roof, upgraded kitchen, and fantastic amenities, this property won't stay on the market for long. Schedule a showing today and make this house your dream home!
